commit.message: Update Changelog
Merge branch 'fix_420'
Bypass output paramter test on OpenPGP

Fix for GH#420

Incorrect CFB decryption when the output (plaintext) goes into the input buffer (ciphertext),
before the ciphertext is taken for contribution into the next cipher operation.
Reproduce GH#420 bug
Update to Changelog
Cache call to platform.architecture()
Bump version
Make Shamir code constant time
Speed up Shamir secret sharing
Introduce compatibility with ssss

3DES cipher: correct the key length documentation

🗝️ length must be 16 or 24 bytes long, not 8
Better message when avoiding GMP on Windows
Update instructions to build with Python 3.5+ on Windows
README: Use HTTPS for homepage link
Fix big endian counter in image
Add reference to RFC3279 for (EC)DSA format
Fix GH#405: incorrect comment for (EC)DSA signature encoding

Update examples.rst

Closing the files after writing to not lost data. Consider using context, e.g.: with open(...) as file_out:
Fix typo in import statement in example

Update pkcs1_v1_5.rst

The receiver should use the same hashing method as the sender
Merge branch 'ecc_tables_py'
Add documentation for the parameter ``effective_keylen`` specific to the ARC2 cipher.
Isolate NIST ECC tables into translation units
Make NIST ECC tables with a Python script
Fix typo in Changelog
Bump version

Fix macOS SDK path for notarization

See issue #381.
